## Minimal Lists

Clean, minimal styling with custom bullet markers:

```css
:root {
  --list-indent: calc(var(--content-spacing) * 0.5);
  --list-item-spacing: var(--space-1);
  --list-marker-content: '• ';
  --list-marker-nested-content: '◦ ';
  --list-marker-color: var(--color-accent);
}
```

